			</p>
			<img id="divergent" src="images/divergent.png" class="fragment fade">

			<p id="thinking2" class="fragment fade">
				<strong>Divergent Thinking</strong> = generating multiple ideas, solutions, or alternatives.
			</p>
			<p id="converget" class="fragment fade">	
				<strong>Convergent Thinking</strong> = evaluating and selecting from among those alternatives.
			</p>
			<p id="design7" class="fragment fade">
				<strong>Divergent Thinking</strong><br>
 					Creativity to see many unique viewpoints
					Creativity to generate solutions from that viewpoint
			</p>
		</section>

 		<section>
			<p>Design is a <font size="44px">way of making</font></p>
			<p class="fragment fade">Capability to understand, analyse, model and test view points</p>
